{"tid":2063283,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"千祈唔好食第一城新開果間 (閒悠。館)","createTime":"2020-06-13T20:33:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-15T06:49:07.000Z","uid":21831,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"08a0aba671e84815c4e11408a3b3c473ebc3d34b","tid":2063283,"uid":21831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T20:33:25.000Z","msg":"我屌你老母成間野都係垃圾<br />\n成間野主食得幾款撈麵同幾個飯，有幾款仲要賣曬<br />\n我同條女叫左碗黑蒜蟹柳撈麵同雞扒腸飯<br />\n我碗飯d飯硬過d生米，雞扒鞋過雞胸，台灣腸仔得兩片<br />\n成碗都勁細碗，仲要賣成$80蚊<br />\n條女叫果碗撈麵仲閪，碗麵鹹過海水，d蟹柳又係一條撕開幾片咁，完全食唔落，仲要賣$6x<br />\n成餐飯得杯罐裝冬瓜茶係飲得落<br />\n<br />\n到比錢果下真係呆左，收$15x，睇番先知道仲要收+1，到而家條氣都係唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d347feb28f520563c3718ed3512db1fd2db92885","tid":2063283,"uid":21831,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T20:34:09.000Z","msg":"有無巴打食過，應該呢幾日新開<br />\n見到周圍d客食到閪口閪面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdebdc27bb519e75192cf19ad7865c7bc24b37a1","tid":2063283,"uid":37197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d347feb28f520563c3718ed3512db1fd2db92885","tid":2063283,"uid":21831,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T20:34:09.000Z","msg":"有無巴打食過，應該呢幾日新開<br />\n見到周圍d客食到閪口閪面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T20:37:25.000Z","msg":"佢個位係以前邊間舖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2f63a5063f959cea9ce957506aa7f76b4412a18","tid":2063283,"uid":21831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fdebdc27bb519e75192cf19ad7865c7bc24b37a1","tid":2063283,"uid":37197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d347feb28f520563c3718ed3512db1fd2db92885","tid":2063283,"uid":21831,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T20:34:09.000Z","msg":"有無巴打食過，應該呢幾日新開<br />\n見到周圍d客食到閪口閪面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T20